CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 20, 1945, pg. 13, reads: "At W. VA. State - Shown above are a group of West Virginia State College students, all residents of Pittsburgh, Pa., who posed for a picture following the West Virginia State-Morgan College football game. Left to right: Beatrice Williams, Doris Corsey, Jesse Holliday, Imogen Withington, Rosie M. Robinson, Doris Clark, Delores Allen, O'Neil Humphreys, Marguerita Coles (center), 'Miss West Virginia State'; Lois Weavers, Elizabeth Mallory, Rosemarie Laurence, Elaine Davis, John Scales, Eunice Walker and Cora Perry."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of West Virginia State College students from Pittsburgh, from left: Beatrice Williams, Doris Corsey, Jesse Holliday, Imogen Withington, Rosie M. Robinson, Doris Clark, Delores Allen, O'Neil Humphreys, Marguerita Coles, Lois Weaver, Elizabeth Mallory, Rosemarie Lawrence, Elaine Davis, John Scales, Eunice Walker, and Cora Perry, gathered at wall on campus
